===Etymology 1===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{term|dere|lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{term/t|ang|dēore}}. Cognate with Dutch {{term|duur||costly, precious|lang=nl}}, German {{term|teuer||costly, precious|lang=de}}, Icelandic {{term|dýr||expensive|lang=is}}, Norwegian [[dyr]], Swedish {{term|dyr||expensive|lang=sv}}.

